HEADWORD: Pectinal
<hw>Pec"ti*nal</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fish whose bones resemble comb
teeth.</def> <rj><au>Sir T. Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

